Per-entry overrides. Each `AssetEntry` in the asset manifest carries its
own `license` field. Permitted values are documented in
`src/asset/preload.ts` and currently include:

  CC-BY-4.0     Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (default).
  CC-BY-SA-4.0  Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International.
                Use for track and community data per GDD section 26.
