When an entry declares `CC-BY-SA-4.0`, the assets it covers and any derivative
works must be distributed under the same license. Mixed-license manifests are
allowed but every entry must declare its own license; the loader rejects any
manifest entry that omits the field.

Attribution. When you reuse a CC BY 4.0 or CC BY-SA 4.0 asset from this
repository, include the asset id and the project name (`VibeGear2`) in your
attribution. A link back to this repository satisfies the attribution
requirement under both licenses.

Originality. Per GDD section 26, every shipped asset must be original work
or correctly licensed work. No copied Top Gear 2 assets, names, or
soundalikes. No "temporary borrowed art." No sample packs with unclear
provenance. Contributions that violate this policy will be reverted before
release.

